poldis 0.0.3

Parse text with NLP

annotate_text.Rd

Wrapper for `spacyr::spacy_parse` function.

annotate_text(v, level = "words")

Arguments

v

Text vector

level

Do you want to parse words or sentences? Words by default.

Examples

# \donttest{
annotate_text(US_News_Conferences_1960_1980[1:2, 3])
